<div class="title">Gentle State of Satisfaction</div>
<div class="substance">2C-B</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=LHT&Exact=1">LHT</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; LHT. "Gentle State of Satisfaction: An Experience with 2C-B (exp107987)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Mar 1, 2016. erowid.org/exp/107987</div>

<br/>



